= DESCRIPTION OF CODE
This MATLAB code is a mex interface for
C code of Xiao-Yu Hu for generating LDPC
code using PEG algorithm of Hu and Arnold.

= USAGE
To use the code compile the mex function by:

>> mex GenerateLDPC_mex.C BigGirth.C CyclesOfGraph.C Random.C GenerateLDPC.C

Then call the function to generate regular LDPC code

>> A = buildLDPCmatrix(252, 504, 3)


